questions: Kun je mij vertellen welke patiënten momenteel hun patiëntportaal hebben geactiveerd?
answers_GPT3_5: SELECT patientrooster.naam, patientrooster.geboortedatum, patientrooster.email, patientrooster.mobiel FROM patient LEFT JOIN (SELECT patient.id, patient.email, patient.mobiel FROM patient INNER JOIN gebruiker on gebruiker.email = patient.email and gebruiker.mobiel = patient.mobiel and gebruiker.geactiveerd = 1) as patientrooster on patient.id = patientrooster.id WHERE patient.system = 'zorgmail' and patient.portaalactivated = 1 and patient.portaalapproved = 1 and patient.portaalblokkeerd = 0 and patient.portaalinformed = 1 and patient.portaaltype = 'patient'
answers_golden_standard: SELECT * FROM patient WHERE ispatientportalactivated = 1

questions: Welke afspraken heeft cliënt Niels Jong gehad?
answers_GPT3_5: SELECT appointment.* FROM patient INNER JOIN appointmentparticipation ON appointmentparticipation.patient_id = patient.id AND appointmentparticipation.interval = 'appointment' LEFT JOIN appointment on appointment.id = appointmentparticipation.appointment_id WHERE patient.name = 'Niels Jong'
answers_golden_standard: SELECT appointment.* FROM appointment LEFT JOIN appointmentparticipation ON appointment.id = appointmentparticipation.appointment_id LEFT JOIN participant ON participant.id = appointmentparticipation.participant_id LEFT JOIN patient ON patient.id = participant.patient_id WHERE patient.ROEPNAAM = 'Niels' and patient.EIGENNAAM = 'Jong'

questions: Kunt u mij alstublieft informeren over de afspraken die cliënt Niels Jong heeft gehad?
answers_GPT3_5: SELECT patient.ZORGACHTERNAAM, appointment.* FROM patient LEFT JOIN appointment on appointment.patient_id = patient.id WHERE patient.ZORGROEPNAAM = 'Annatommie' and patient.ZORGACHTERNAAM = 'Jong' and appointment.interval = 30
answers_golden_standard: SELECT appointment.* FROM appointment LEFT JOIN appointmentparticipation ON appointment.id = appointmentparticipation.appointment_id LEFT JOIN participant ON participant.id = appointmentparticipation.participant_id LEFT JOIN patient ON patient.id = participant.patient_id WHERE patient.ROEPNAAM = 'Niels' and patient.EIGENNAAM = 'Jong'
